2
00:00:09,690 --> 00:00:11,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak menyangka ini terjadi?</font>

3
00:00:11,990 --> 00:00:13,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak sama sekali.</font>

4
00:00:14,560 --> 00:00:18,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Daebi Mama berkata aku hanya perlu lolos sampai babak kedua.</font>

5
00:00:21,360 --> 00:00:23,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila aku menjadi Selir Kerajaan..</font>

6
00:00:24,890 --> 00:00:28,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimanapun, aku harus segera bertemu Daebi Mama.</font>

7
00:00:29,030 --> 00:00:31,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau masih memercayai Daebi Mama?</font>

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:34,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia adalah ahli dalam memanfaatkan orang demi kepentingannya.</font>

9
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan upaya pembunuhan...</font>

10
00:00:36,730 --> 00:00:40,030
<font color=#FFFF00>...Doryongnim di istana, Daebi Mama pelakunya.</font>

11
00:00:47,590 --> 00:00:48,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi.</font>

12
00:00:50,830 --> 00:00:52,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memercayai Doryongnim, 'kan?</font>

13
00:00:56,090 --> 00:00:59,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Percayalah pada pria yang kau cintai
dan tunggu sebentar lagi.</font>

14
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:09,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti yang kujanjikan,
Dayang Han lolos seleksi tahap ketiga.</font>

15
00:01:10,060 --> 00:01:14,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, giliran Jusang memenuhi keinginan ibumu ini.</font>

16
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:17,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, sebagaimana saya janjikan,</font>

17
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:21,630
<font color=#FFFF00>saya akan membantu Putri Busang menjadi Ratu.</font>

18
00:01:22,330 --> 00:01:24,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Belakangan ini, Raja semakin sering menemui Daebi.</font>

19
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya yakin bahwa...</font>

20
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:28,730
<font color=#FFFF00>...dalam seleksi ini, dia memihak Daebi.</font>

21
00:01:28,730 --> 00:01:30,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Seleksi tahap ketiga masih lama...</font>

22
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:33,160
<font color=#FFFF00>namun sudah ada rumor bahwa posisi Ratu...</font>

23
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:35,330
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan dimenangkan oleh putrinya Busang.</font>

24
00:01:39,460 --> 00:01:41,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah ini karena Ga Eun lagi?</font>

25
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:45,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, kelihatannya bila anak itu dijadikan Selir,</font>

26
00:01:45,590 --> 00:01:47,660
<font color=#FFFF00>maka putrinya Busang akan menjadi Ratu,</font>

27
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,560
<font color=#FFFF00>itulah perjanjian Daebi dengan Raja.</font>

28
00:01:49,630 --> 00:01:53,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika ini benar terjadi,
maka seleksi itu tidak ada gunanya lagi (sudah jelas pemenangnya).</font>

29
00:01:55,354 --> 00:02:00,354
<font color=#FFFF00>Penerjemah .: Writer Ayra :.</font>

30
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:04,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Tahap ketiga...</font>

31
00:02:04,730 --> 00:02:06,660
<font color=#FFFF00>...hanyalah formalitas belaka.</font>

32
00:02:06,660 --> 00:02:10,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Mama, apakah sungguh putri saya akan menjadi Ratu?</font>

33
00:02:12,630 --> 00:02:14,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Secara teknis begitu.</font>

34
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:18,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Segera, kau akan menjadi mertua Raja.</font>

35
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:26,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah tidak ada cara lain untuk membatalkan hasil seleksi?</font>

36
00:02:26,890 --> 00:02:28,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan hamba, Jeoha.</font>

37
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:34,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mencoba membujuk Lee Sun.</font>

38
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:36,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tidak ada gunanya.</font>

39
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:40,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia telah melanggar janji kami,</font>

40
00:02:41,890 --> 00:02:45,460
<font color=#FFFF00>sebab Lee Sun sudah membulatkan tekadnya.</font>

41
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:57,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah menyuruhmu berhati-hati.</font>

42
00:03:00,790 --> 00:03:02,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah ada yang mendesak?</font>

43
00:03:12,790 --> 00:03:15,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Cara mengeluarkan Ga Eun..</font>

44
00:03:16,260 --> 00:03:17,830
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku harus menemukannya.</font>

45
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:19,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Jeoha.</font>

46
00:03:23,330 --> 00:03:25,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin Dayang Han merasa nyaman.</font>

47
00:03:25,830 --> 00:03:28,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Layani dia dengan segala sesuatu yang mungkin dia butuhkan.</font>

48
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:30,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik, Cheonha.</font>

49
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:50,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

50
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:52,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Busang Doryongnim (Kepala Pedagang Keliling)
mengirim hadiah untuk Anda.</font>

51
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukalah.</font>

52
00:04:18,330 --> 00:04:22,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun-ah, sejak aku mengetahui kau ketergantungan pil poppi,</font>

53
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:25,860
<font color=#FFFF00>setiap hari aku terus mencari penawarnya.</font>

54
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:28,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Akhirnya, aku menemukannya.</font>

55
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:32,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Minumlah ini dan atasi ketergantunganmu.</font>

56
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:44,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha, pil apa ini?</font>

57
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:47,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Penawar pil poppi.</font>

58
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:50,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Sungguh ini penawarnya?</font>

59
00:04:52,230 --> 00:04:55,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryong bilang begitu.</font>

60
00:04:55,330 --> 00:04:56,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun satu-satunya yang tahu formula penawarnya...</font>

61
00:04:56,930 --> 00:04:58,930
<font color=#FFFF00>....adalah Dae Mok dari Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

62
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:02,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa Doryong mendapatkannya?</font>

63
00:05:04,030 --> 00:05:06,760
<font color=#FFFF00>- Itu...
- Apa Anda sungguh memercayainya?</font>

64
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan hamba, Cheonha.</font>

65
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:13,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Hamba sempat melihatnya penuh tatapan ketidaksetiaan.</font>

66
00:05:15,900 --> 00:05:17,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan kau melihatnya?</font>

67
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:20,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat Paduka memberikan jubah kepada Dayang Han.</font>

68
00:05:30,090 --> 00:05:32,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha, ada dua pil.</font>

69
00:05:32,090 --> 00:05:35,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila Anda hendak meminumnya,
lebih baik dayang pencoba
(dayang yang bertugas mencicipi segala sesuatu
yang disajikan kepada Raja) yang melakukannya dulu.</font>

70
00:05:35,630 --> 00:05:38,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu memang sudah tugasnya mencoba dulu apa pun..</font>

71
00:05:38,330 --> 00:05:39,990
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang disajikan pada Anda.</font>

72
00:05:54,330 --> 00:05:55,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah sendok peraknya aman?</font>

73
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Cheonha.</font>

74
00:05:59,030 --> 00:06:00,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kelihatannya tidak beracun.</font>

75
00:06:15,490 --> 00:06:17,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Hamba yakin aman untuk dikonsumsi.</font>

76
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:30,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha.</font>

77
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:45,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Panggil tabib istana! Cepat!</font>

78
00:06:54,090 --> 00:06:55,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah tewas.</font>

79
00:07:35,930 --> 00:07:38,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus memindahnya jasadnya diam-diam.</font>

80
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:40,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia menyebutku temannya,</font>

81
00:07:42,290 --> 00:07:44,460
<font color=#FFFF00>dan kematian ayahku pun...</font>

82
00:07:45,130 --> 00:07:46,830
<font color=#FFFF00>...katanya akan dibalaskan.</font>

83
00:07:49,590 --> 00:07:51,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memercayai ucapannya,</font>

84
00:07:53,060 --> 00:07:56,190
<font color=#FFFF00>namun dia coba membunuhku.</font>

85
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:05,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak ada bedanya dengan para bajingan yang membunuh ayahku.</font>

86
00:08:06,290 --> 00:08:09,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mungkin menganggapku hewan buas
yang bisa dibunuh setiap saat.</font>

87
00:08:11,130 --> 00:08:12,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

88
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:15,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejak awal...</font>

89
00:08:16,890 --> 00:08:21,090
<font color=#FFFF00>...mungkin dia tidak ingin aku tetap hidup.</font>

90
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:24,860
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku!!!
- Che... Cheonha, mohon tenang.</font>

91
00:08:24,930 --> 00:08:27,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyeon Seok-ah, kau percaya padaku?</font>

92
00:08:28,930 --> 00:08:30,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Cheonha.</font>

93
00:08:30,030 --> 00:08:33,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga memercayaimu.
Jika bukan berkatmu,</font>

94
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:36,090
<font color=#FFFF00>bukannya Seo Sanggung, tapi aku...</font>

95
00:08:36,090 --> 00:08:38,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang akan tewas mengenaskan tadi.</font>

96
00:08:38,130 --> 00:08:39,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha.</font>

97
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:43,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Seok-ah, kau bilang bagimu, aku...</font>

98
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,760
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah Raja sesungguhnya, 'kan?</font>

99
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:47,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Cheonha.</font>

100
00:08:47,190 --> 00:08:50,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagi hamba, Anda adalah Raja sejati.</font>

101
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:52,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan bila Seja yang sudah mati...</font>

102
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:55,960
<font color=#FFFF00>...rupanya masih hidup?</font>

103
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Busang Doryong itu...</font>

104
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:03,360
<font color=#FFFF00>..adalah Seja yang asli.</font>

105
00:09:05,090 --> 00:09:08,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang yang berhak menduduki singgasana...</font>

106
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:10,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja yang asli.</font>

107
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:21,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus pergi ke suatu tempat.</font>

108
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:33,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kiranya yang membuat Jusang Cheonha kemari
larut malam begini?</font>

109
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:37,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya ingin menjadi Raja.</font>

110
00:09:39,430 --> 00:09:42,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya... ingin...</font>

111
00:09:44,830 --> 00:09:46,590
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjadi Raja sesungguhnya.</font>

112
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja...</font>

113
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:54,160
<font color=#FFFF00>...sesungguhnya, katamu?</font>

114
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:58,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, bila Anda menjadikan saya Raja sesungguhnya,</font>

115
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:01,360
<font color=#FFFF00>saya akan menyetujui apa pun yang diinginkan Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

116
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:06,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kau kan sudah menjadi Raja.</font>

117
00:10:07,330 --> 00:10:08,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya...</font>

118
00:10:11,930 --> 00:10:13,660
<font color=#FFFF00>...Raja palsu.</font>

119
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:15,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang yang palsu ingin menjadi asli?</font>

120
00:10:18,130 --> 00:10:19,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana caranya?</font>

121
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingin melepas topeng itu...</font>

122
00:10:22,590 --> 00:10:25,500
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menunjukkan wajah aslimu di hadapan semua orang?</font>

123
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:28,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Ataukah kau ingin menjadikanku batu loncatan...</font>

124
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:31,500
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk berhenti menjadi boneka,
kemudian sepenuhnya Raja merdeka?</font>

125
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:32,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan seperti itu.</font>

126
00:10:32,690 --> 00:10:34,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau bukan begitu,</font>

127
00:10:35,830 --> 00:10:37,130
<font color=#FFFF00>lalu apa tepatnya?</font>

128
00:10:42,090 --> 00:10:44,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Agar saya bisa berhenti menjadi palsu,</font>

129
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:52,460
<font color=#FFFF00>yang asli...</font>

130
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:54,930
<font color=#FFFF00>..harus mati.</font>

131
00:10:59,130 --> 00:11:00,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

132
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:03,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja yang asli...</font>

133
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:05,530
<font color=#FFFF00>...masih hidup.</font>

134
00:11:22,660 --> 00:11:25,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengurus Jang, Kau lihat Gon?</font>

135
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:26,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Daepyunsoo Eureushin,</font>

136
00:11:27,230 --> 00:11:29,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok Eureushin ingin bertemu dengan Anda.</font>

137
00:11:42,630 --> 00:11:44,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Gon-ah! Gon-ah!</font>

138
00:11:47,730 --> 00:11:50,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji!
Kenapa melakukan hal ini?</font>

139
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:52,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Gon adalah orangku!
Kalau dia bersalah, aku yang berhak menghukumnya.</font>

140
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah sebabnya aku...</font>

141
00:11:55,660 --> 00:11:57,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak langsung membunuhnya.</font>

142
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:01,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia adalah orangmu,</font>

143
00:12:02,990 --> 00:12:04,360
<font color=#FFFF00>jadi kau yang bunuh!</font>

144
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:08,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji. Ada apa sebenarnya ini?</font>

145
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Telah menipu kakekmu ini...</font>

146
00:12:11,990 --> 00:12:13,390
<font color=#FFFF00>...apa kau bisa menanggung akibatnya?</font>

147
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:17,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau kau akan memilih membunuh Gon
dan menghindari hukumanmu?</font>

148
00:12:19,030 --> 00:12:20,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua petarung Pyunsoo...</font>

149
00:12:21,460 --> 00:12:24,030
<font color=#FFFF00>...memiliki ramuan untuk menyembunyikan denyut nadi.</font>

150
00:12:24,930 --> 00:12:26,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Malam itu,</font>

151
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:29,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Gon juga membawanya.</font>

152
00:12:30,690 --> 00:12:33,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti amat bersyukur karena itu.</font>

153
00:12:34,530 --> 00:12:36,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak mengerti apa maksudnya semua itu.</font>

154
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:39,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dan siapa yang bicara
sampai Gon diperlakukan seperti ini?</font>

155
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:43,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang aku sudah tahu alasan asli kau menjadi Daepyunsoo!</font>

156
00:12:49,860 --> 00:12:51,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang Gon katakan?</font>

157
00:12:51,890 --> 00:12:53,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahwa aku menipu Harabeoji?</font>

158
00:12:53,890 --> 00:12:55,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Gon...</font>

159
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:58,760
<font color=#FFFF00>...menolak bicara sampai akhir.</font>

160
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:00,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu kenapa melakukan ini padanya?</font>

161
00:13:00,190 --> 00:13:01,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Hwa Gun-ah!</font>

162
00:13:05,930 --> 00:13:07,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Gon adalah orangmu.</font>

163
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:11,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun kakekmu punya lebih banyak orang.</font>

164
00:13:11,830 --> 00:13:14,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu? Apa yang orang Harabeoji katakan?</font>

165
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:16,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Busang Doryong...</font>

166
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:20,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah Seja yang asli.</font>

167
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:24,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa orang yang coba aku, Dae Mok, bunuh...</font>

168
00:13:25,230 --> 00:13:27,360
<font color=#FFFF00>...diselamatkan oleh...</font>

169
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,490
<font color=#FFFF00>...cucuku sendiri?</font>

170
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:34,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Omong kosong macam apa itu?</font>

171
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:40,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Hwa Gun.</font>

172
00:13:41,930 --> 00:13:44,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Abeonim, ada apa?</font>

173
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:56,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Hwa Gun-ah. Kuberi kau satu kesempatan lagi.</font>

174
00:13:57,990 --> 00:13:59,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada yang ingin kau katakan pada kakekmu ini?</font>

175
00:14:07,730 --> 00:14:09,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Busang Doryongnim,</font>

176
00:14:09,590 --> 00:14:11,760
<font color=#FFFF00>sekalipun dia memang Seja asli,</font>

177
00:14:12,330 --> 00:14:13,860
<font color=#FFFF00>tak akan ada yang berubah.</font>

178
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:17,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji sudah berjanji padaku.</font>

179
00:14:17,730 --> 00:14:22,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Janji bahwa tidak akan melukai Seja Jeoha.</font>

180
00:14:23,860 --> 00:14:24,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu benar.</font>

181
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Memang begitu.</font>

182
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:32,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika janji itu dilanggar,</font>

183
00:14:32,290 --> 00:14:34,230
<font color=#FFFF00>dan Seja Jeoha terbunuh,</font>

184
00:14:37,430 --> 00:14:39,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji akan menyaksikan langsung kematianku.</font>

185
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:40,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Hwa Gun-ah.</font>

186
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:51,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Abeonim, dia masih kekanakan.</font>

187
00:14:51,290 --> 00:14:53,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya akan bicara padanya,
saya mohon...</font>

188
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:54,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Penjaga!</font>

189
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:58,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Kunci dia di kamarnya!
Jangan biarkan dia keluar tanpa izinku.</font>

190
00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:59,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

191
00:14:59,090 --> 00:15:02,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji, aku akan memenangkan hati Seja Jeoha.</font>

192
00:15:02,390 --> 00:15:04,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong biarkan Jeoha hidup!</font>

193
00:15:04,090 --> 00:15:06,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji! Tolong biarkan Jeoha hidup!</font>

194
00:15:07,590 --> 00:15:11,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Biarkan dia hidup. Harabeoji! Kumohon!</font>

195
00:15:11,090 --> 00:15:12,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji!</font>

196
00:15:16,990 --> 00:15:18,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Mama-nim.</font>

197
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:22,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin minta tolong...</font>

198
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:24,390
<font color=#FFFF00>...hal yang sulit.</font>

199
00:15:42,460 --> 00:15:43,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim...</font>

200
00:15:44,690 --> 00:15:47,160
<font color=#FFFF00>...memintaku menyampaikan surat ini.</font>

201
00:15:59,290 --> 00:16:01,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang Doryongnim katakan?</font>

202
00:16:01,430 --> 00:16:04,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Malam ini, dia akan membawaku.</font>

203
00:16:26,130 --> 00:16:27,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunjukkan wajahmu!</font>

204
00:16:30,190 --> 00:16:31,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang!</font>

205
00:16:42,290 --> 00:16:43,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa seperti ini?</font>

206
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:54,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha, mereka melanggar perintah kerajaan...</font>

207
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,260
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang melarang dayang meninggalkan istana.</font>

208
00:16:56,430 --> 00:16:57,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Kerja bagus.</font>

209
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:09,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau ingin keluar...</font>

210
00:17:10,730 --> 00:17:12,560
<font color=#FFFF00>...tanpa izinku?</font>

211
00:17:14,590 --> 00:17:15,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha.</font>

212
00:17:16,090 --> 00:17:17,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Mama-nim tidak bersalah.</font>

213
00:17:18,230 --> 00:17:20,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong hukum saya saja,</font>

214
00:17:20,230 --> 00:17:22,730
<font color=#FFFF00>dan ampuni Mama-nim.</font>

215
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:24,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

216
00:17:26,330 --> 00:17:28,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mengampuninya.</font>

217
00:17:31,130 --> 00:17:33,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau punya keinginan lain?</font>

218
00:17:36,990 --> 00:17:38,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikuti aku.</font>

219
00:18:00,530 --> 00:18:02,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau lupa yang sudah kukatakan padamu?</font>

220
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:04,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau terus berusaha membantu Seja?</font>

221
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:06,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa...</font>

222
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:09,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...saya tidak boleh membantunya?</font>

223
00:18:09,860 --> 00:18:11,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kau berkata begitu setelah yang baru saja terjadi?</font>

224
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:13,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Namanya Yang.</font>

225
00:18:14,130 --> 00:18:17,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak yang berhasil membuat saya tergerak menggambar peta itu,
namanya adalah...</font>

226
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:20,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang.</font>

227
00:18:21,860 --> 00:18:23,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Hati saya yang telah beku setelah menjadi penonton sekian lama,
tergerak oleh...</font>

228
00:18:24,530 --> 00:18:26,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...anak itu.</font>

229
00:18:28,090 --> 00:18:29,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Abeoji.</font>

230
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:35,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan sekarang,
masih banyak anak-anak di ladang poppi itu.</font>

231
00:18:36,460 --> 00:18:39,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang yang dapat melawan Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

232
00:18:39,930 --> 00:18:41,590
<font color=#FFFF00>dan memiliki tekad melakukannya...</font>

233
00:18:42,090 --> 00:18:44,130
<font color=#FFFF00>..di Joseon ini adalah dia, Seja Jeoha.</font>

234
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia satu-satunya dia di negeri ini.</font>

235
00:18:47,430 --> 00:18:48,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang sebenarnya ingin kau lakukan?</font>

236
00:18:48,990 --> 00:18:51,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebagaimana kegigihan anak itu telah menggerakkan hati saya,</font>

237
00:18:52,230 --> 00:18:54,090
<font color=#FFFF00>saya akan coba menggerakkan hati...</font>

238
00:18:54,090 --> 00:18:55,760
<font color=#FFFF00>...Abeoji dengan kesungguhan saya.</font>

239
00:18:58,130 --> 00:18:59,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Abeoji.</font>

240
00:19:00,330 --> 00:19:03,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong, bantulah Seja Jeoha.</font>

241
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:19,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Hamba siap menerima...</font>

242
00:19:19,830 --> 00:19:21,130
<font color=#FFFF00>..hukuman apa pun.</font>

243
00:19:26,060 --> 00:19:27,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi.</font>

244
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:32,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kau sama sekali tidak mengenaliku?</font>

245
00:19:35,760 --> 00:19:37,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku dan Aghassi...</font>

246
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:41,530
<font color=#FFFF00>...menghabiskan banyak waktu bersama.</font>

247
00:19:43,890 --> 00:19:45,760
<font color=#FFFF00>- Cheonha...
- Belum jugakah...</font>

248
00:19:46,460 --> 00:19:47,760
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau mengenaliku?</font>

249
00:20:01,700 --> 00:20:03,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha, tolong jangan lakukan.</font>

250
00:20:10,430 --> 00:20:11,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi.</font>

251
00:20:12,630 --> 00:20:13,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku,</font>

252
00:20:15,130 --> 00:20:16,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun.</font>

253
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:38,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun-ah.</font>

254
00:20:40,260 --> 00:20:41,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau...</font>

255
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:46,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini mimpi, 'kan?</font>

256
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:48,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini...</font>

257
00:20:49,530 --> 00:20:50,560
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukan mimpi.</font>

258
00:20:51,330 --> 00:20:52,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh...</font>

259
00:20:53,060 --> 00:20:54,090
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau Lee Sun?</font>

260
00:20:54,290 --> 00:20:55,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

261
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Kawan kecil Aghassi,</font>

262
00:20:58,630 --> 00:21:00,130
<font color=#FFFF00>benar Lee Sun yang itu.</font>

263
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:05,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menunggumu sekian lama.</font>

264
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:08,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku, Imo, juga Kko Mool...</font>

265
00:21:08,260 --> 00:21:09,990
<font color=#FFFF00>...menunggumu sekian lama.</font>

266
00:21:11,060 --> 00:21:12,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga...</font>

267
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:14,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...menunggu.</font>

268
00:21:23,090 --> 00:21:24,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

269
00:21:25,730 --> 00:21:26,730
<font color=#FFFF00>...kenapa...</font>

270
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:28,930
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau di sini?</font>

271
00:21:30,760 --> 00:21:33,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun, kenapa kau memakai topeng itu di sini?</font>

272
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:36,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun-ah.</font>

273
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Lima tahun lalu,</font>

274
00:21:46,990 --> 00:21:48,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja yang asli...</font>

275
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:52,090
<font color=#FFFF00>...membuatku memakai topeng ini,</font>

276
00:21:53,490 --> 00:21:54,990
<font color=#FFFF00>dan melarikan diri.</font>

277
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:01,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejak itulah,</font>

278
00:22:04,530 --> 00:22:06,960
<font color=#FFFF00>aku terus ditekan Dae Mok...</font>

279
00:22:10,760 --> 00:22:12,660
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan berpura-pura menjadi Raja.</font>

280
00:22:14,290 --> 00:22:15,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja...</font>

281
00:22:17,190 --> 00:22:19,230
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidakkah cukup baginya membunuh ayahku?</font>

282
00:22:19,930 --> 00:22:21,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia membuatmu melakukan hal itu juga?</font>

283
00:22:21,860 --> 00:22:22,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

284
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:25,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja...</font>

285
00:22:27,360 --> 00:22:28,590
<font color=#FFFF00>...melakukannya.</font>

286
00:22:28,930 --> 00:22:30,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak memberitahuku lebih awal?</font>

287
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:32,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak menyangka...</font>

288
00:22:33,760 --> 00:22:35,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan terus mengira kau pembunuh ayahku.</font>

289
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:38,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau menyembunyikannya dariku?</font>

290
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:43,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Se... Seja Jeoha...</font>

291
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:49,030
<font color=#FFFF00>...melarangku mengatakan kebenarannya pada Aghassi.</font>

292
00:22:55,260 --> 00:22:56,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja...</font>

293
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:01,760
<font color=#FFFF00>...melarangmu jujur padaku?</font>

294
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

295
00:23:04,830 --> 00:23:07,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi... mengenalnya.</font>

296
00:23:13,030 --> 00:23:15,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi, Oh Busang Doryong...</font>

297
00:23:17,330 --> 00:23:18,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria itu...</font>

298
00:23:20,390 --> 00:23:21,890
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah Seja yang asli.</font>

299
00:23:25,690 --> 00:23:27,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria yang Aghassi kira Chun Soo.</font>

300
00:23:28,890 --> 00:23:30,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Dialah yang membunuh Gyu Ho Eureushin.</font>

301
00:23:39,090 --> 00:23:40,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Chun Soo Doryongnim...</font>

302
00:23:43,360 --> 00:23:44,390
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah...</font>

303
00:23:45,860 --> 00:23:46,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...Seja asli?</font>

304
00:23:47,930 --> 00:23:48,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

305
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:52,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak mungkin.</font>

306
00:23:55,260 --> 00:23:56,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasti ada kesalahpahaman.</font>

307
00:23:58,460 --> 00:24:00,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Chun Soo Doryongnim tidak mungkin Seja.</font>

308
00:24:01,490 --> 00:24:03,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun, kau pasti salah paham.</font>

309
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:13,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Chun Soo Doryongnim...</font>

310
00:24:15,930 --> 00:24:17,460
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah Oh Busang Doryongnim.</font>

311
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:20,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

312
00:24:21,990 --> 00:24:23,330
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku mencintainya.</font>

313
00:24:30,290 --> 00:24:31,360
<font color=#FFFF00>- Tidak.
- Aku...</font>

314
00:24:32,030 --> 00:24:34,390
<font color=#FFFF00>...semestinya lebih cepat jujur padamu.</font>

315
00:24:36,590 --> 00:24:37,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

316
00:24:39,390 --> 00:24:40,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh...</font>

317
00:24:43,060 --> 00:24:44,390
<font color=#FFFF00>...Chun Soo Doryongnim...</font>

318
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:47,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah Seja?</font>

319
00:24:47,760 --> 00:24:48,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

320
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:07,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun di mana?</font>

321
00:25:07,390 --> 00:25:08,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

322
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:13,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak bisa datang karena kami tertangkap di gerbang.</font>

323
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:15,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menjemputnya.</font>

324
00:25:15,130 --> 00:25:16,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengawal dimana-mana.</font>

325
00:25:16,990 --> 00:25:19,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Terlalu berbahaya menyusup ke dalam istana.</font>

326
00:25:19,230 --> 00:25:20,830
<font color=#FFFF00>- Tapi.
- Chun Soo Doryongnim.</font>

327
00:25:28,990 --> 00:25:30,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah.</font>

328
00:25:31,760 --> 00:25:32,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau selamat.</font>

329
00:25:34,460 --> 00:25:35,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun Aghassi.</font>

330
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:38,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana... bisa keluar?</font>

331
00:25:39,430 --> 00:25:40,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bertemu teman masa kecilku,</font>

332
00:25:41,930 --> 00:25:43,690
<font color=#FFFF00>dan dia membantuku keluar dengan selamat.</font>

333
00:25:47,190 --> 00:25:50,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah, ayo cepat sebelum matahari terbit.</font>

334
00:25:55,630 --> 00:25:57,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih sudah membantu kami.</font>

335
00:25:58,460 --> 00:26:01,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami tidak akan melupakan kebaikanmu.</font>

336
00:26:10,760 --> 00:26:12,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, tolong hati-hati di jalan.</font>

337
00:26:28,690 --> 00:26:29,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah.</font>

338
00:26:31,030 --> 00:26:33,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah terjadi sesuatu?</font>

339
00:26:35,830 --> 00:26:38,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lupa membawa sesuatu yang penting.</font>

340
00:26:42,430 --> 00:26:46,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa kau ikut denganku sebentar?</font>

341
00:27:16,030 --> 00:27:18,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang lupa membawa sesuatu yang penting.</font>

342
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:23,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau bisa mendapatkan kunci rumah hijau ini?</font>

343
00:27:25,760 --> 00:27:26,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Di sini.</font>

344
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:31,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah yang lebih penting dari nyawaku sendiri.</font>

345
00:27:34,860 --> 00:27:37,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim ingin melihatnya?</font>

346
00:27:40,914 --> 00:27:45,914
<font color=#FFFF00>Penerjemah .: Writer Ayra :.</font>

347
00:27:56,760 --> 00:27:59,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Hakim Hanseungbo Han Gyu Ho dan Petugas Park Moo Ha,</font>

348
00:27:59,960 --> 00:28:03,290
<font color=#FFFF00>sekarang aku memerintahkan penyelidikan mendalam
atas Yangsucheong.</font>

349
00:28:03,290 --> 00:28:07,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya, Han Gyu Ho,
