356
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:40,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari itu,</font>

357
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:44,260
<font color=#FFFF00>hidupku berubah.</font>

358
00:28:46,060 --> 00:28:47,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga...</font>

359
00:28:48,990 --> 00:28:52,630
<font color=#FFFF00>..hari demi hari melalui kesulitan, karena Doryongnim...</font>

360
00:28:52,690 --> 00:28:54,160
