362
00:29:02,460 --> 00:29:03,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Chun Soo Doryongnim.</font>

363
00:29:06,390 --> 00:29:07,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim...</font>

364
00:29:09,990 --> 00:29:12,190
<font color=#FFFF00>...pemilik rumah hijau ini?</font>

365
00:29:14,630 --> 00:29:16,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim benarkah kau...</font>

366
00:29:18,190 --> 00:29:19,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang membunuh ayahku,</font>

367
00:29:21,190 --> 00:29:23,260
<font color=#FFFF00>yaitu... Seja Jeoha?</font>

